						检测项目<span>(5)</span>
					</a>
				</li>
				<li class="mui-table-view-cell">
					<a href="" class="mui-navigate-right">
						常见问题<span>(10)</span>
					</a>
				</li>
				<li class="mui-table-view-cell">
					<a href="" class="mui-navigate-right">
						历史评价<span>(6)</span>
					</a>
				</li>
			</ul>
